title: News – Guns N' Roses
snippet: Ahead of their 2026 World Tour, Guns n' Roses have released “Nothin’” and “Atlas,” their first new music in more than two years. The new tracks join “The General” and “Perhaps” as fresh additions to a classic setlist that will anchor 31+ dates across the globe.
